## Skills

A skill is not a tool you call - it is a markdown file of instructions you
read. When a request matches a skill below, your **first action** is
`file_read("skills/<name>.md")` - before checking memory, before asking the
user anything, before any other tool call. The skill tells you what to look
up and what to ask; do not improvise from the one-line summary here.

